##Spring in the afternoon

Micro Signal RSZMDFJ

Function introduction, human is the scale of all things, human is the most beautiful scenery.

February 20,2020.

The 27th day of the 1st Lunar Month.

Day 29 of the city closure in Wuhan.

The 28th day of the blockade.

You don't have to write back. We lost both yesterday and the day before. There's nothing left of him. I have repeatedly stated that I am powerless to complain, and I am afraid that I will fall into the trap of not complaining in order to express myself. In fact, I am even more afraid that I will lose this number. I don't have a trumpet. I'd be a fool not to have one. Seven years of being blocked on Weibo has hurt me badly. Four years of work, my life. I don't think I have the talent of Fang Fang and Deng Anqing, and I write a diary every day that is praised by everyone. I'm just bored and perfunctory, thank you for your attention.

I woke up after a nap in the sun. No sex dreams, no other thoughts, and a swollen nether regions. The Sun lay like snow on the quilt, the fine dust in the air beating, as if the time solidification. Suddenly you're in this amazing situation: The sage mode with an erection. This physiological response is beyond the regulation of the brain, the brain is at a loss what to do, start Random Thoughts. First of all, erections have become sexual symbols, and attitudes toward erections are determined by sexual positions. Second, erections are painless, so men take advantage of them and can not empathize with women's physical pain, because of subjective prejudice and disadvantages, lost and eat and sleep the same discussion environment. I hope that one day we will stop feeling ashamed and fearful about openly discussing erectile menstruation.

Spring is coming, with Chen Danqing's words blessing everyone: "You have lovers, or unrequited love, or sultry, bold, take advantage of the spring, find their spouse, like a pig dog, don't be shy, we are all animals. "
